{"tid":1464122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係勝利球迷, 下下都見抗爭者比人打柒, 點撐?","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:30:08.000Z","uid":118082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3f8dbcf18e19b1c8e08b520ac6707a51a5a1be97","tid":1464122,"uid":118082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:26:44.000Z","msg":"好多人都係睇形勢去take side<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次經過連儂牆, 都係見到黑警幾惡咁打人既poster<br />\n如果我幫手支持上前線, 容乜易比人打埋一份?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果poster 上面講既係:<br />\n1. 研究顯示支持抗爭者學歷/智商更高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 抗爭者動員能力極高, 可以輕鬆坦緩地鐵 / 機場 / 經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 人民幣急瀉, 中共無力應付美國貿易戰, 經濟勢必衰退, 抗爭四起難以控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要比人知道支持抗爭者係有贏既機會, 先會押注, 而且亦都比同路人信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就好似8月5罷工宣傳, 已經有50萬人響應了, 你會加入嗎??? 一樣道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36efb54a2e79b2edbcbb0225b3af23df3b1dfe46","tid":1464122,"uid":118082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:28:45.000Z","msg":"文宣要比埋自己人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e36ee0e591431a348fcddc3e42e44672453f547","tid":1464122,"uid":118082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:29:02.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af1197089fad86421598201e5e04123853e7740","tid":1464122,"uid":118082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:30:08.000Z","msg":"贏開有條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />